we can have n number of nodes of broker
Ex: If we order the food and we can see where is the deliver partner that is through kafka 

1. distributed streaming platform
2. real time event driven application
3. fault tolerance
4. scalable
5. kafka runs a cluster

the messages are sent by kafka are stored for several days

Kafka Producer : Producer is the one who sends the data to Kafka cluster 

Kafka Consumer : Consumer is the one who consumes the data coming from Kafka cluster

Kafka Clsuter : Kafka Cluster divided into Kafka Brokers, 

Zookeeper : Monitor the health of Kafka Cluster

Kafka Connect : To bring the external data to the cluster from DB or my files without writing data
It has 2 parts Source and Sink - Source - to get the data, Sink - to store the data from cluster

Kafka Stream: 

Start Zookeeper    :        zookeeper-server-start.bat ..\..\config\zookeeper.properties

Start Kafka Broker :        kafka-server-start.bat ..\..\config\server.properties

Create Topic       :        kafka-topics.bat --create --topic my-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 3

Start Producer     :        kafka-console-producer.bat --broker-list localhost:9092 --topic my-topic 

Start Consumer     :        kafka-console-consumer.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic my-topic --from-beginning

